      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Providing rental information for Revaluation 2023
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Revaluation 2023 is underway. It’s important to submit your rental information now to make sure your business rates are accurate.</p>

  </div>
</div>

